title: Elections & Women in Politics Expert Leonie Huddy Available
text:
Elections & Women in Politics Expert Leonie Huddy Available Released: 13-Oct-2015 2:05 PM EDT Contact Information 
  
Leonie Huddy is a Professor in the Department of Political Science at Stony Brook University. Huddy is an expert in elections, public opinion and voting behavior, political psychology, and women and politics Research. 
Huddy has been featured in Australian TV and is a regular exit poll analyst for national CBS radio.
